=Description=

John Restakis:

"Founded by a group of young professionals in 1999, Cooperativa La Fabbrica del Sole has created over the last 10 years a group of companies that work in synergy in the field of renewable energies and environmental sustainability.

La Fabbrica del Sole's mission is to research and spread the off-grid paradigm around the world by designing innovative, eco-friendly and accessible solutions."

